ll, "can_del": false, "cid": 315214, "create_time": 1658896388, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 2020年，中国天然气进口来源呈多元化特点，进口LNG的来源国共24个，有利于提高天然气进口量，保证国家能源安全。其中澳大利亚进口量仍居首位，进口量占比46%。卡塔尔居第二位，其后是马来西亚和印度尼西亚。进口管道气来源国前五名分别为土库曼斯坦、乌兹别克斯坦、哈萨克斯坦、缅甸、俄罗斯。", "timestamp": 1658896388}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 315218, "create_time": 1658896427, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 其他的煤炭还有金属等大宗商品大头是从澳大利亚、印尼等国家进口的", "timestamp": 1658896427}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 315221, "create_time": 1658896466, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 总之，对于其他国家，发展得好的时候就是政策得当，发展得不好的时候就是禀赋限制;  但对于中国，发展不好就是政策不得当。", "timestamp": 1658896466}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 315223, "create_time": 1658896528, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 中国的石油进口最多来自沙特，来源比较多样化", "timestamp": 1658896528}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 315224, "create_time": 1658896530, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Carol: 确实，因为中国真的就应该发展得很好才对🙃", "timestamp": 1658896530}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 315226, "create_time": 1658896568, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 你这不恰好证明了我国能源安全比欧洲强么.", "timestamp": 1658896568}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 315229, "create_time": 1658896646, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "其他国家怎么找的出来这么会经商的商人，这么忍辱负重的工人，这么老实的农民呢😙", "timestamp": 1658896646}], "create_time": 1658889633, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658896646, "likenum": 10, "n_attentions": 10, "